{"arkId":"cl010259099","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010259099","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"l\u00e9cythe","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"l\u00e9cythe"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : classique ; fond blanc II\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 2e quart Ve s. av. J.-C. (-475 - -450)","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":-475,"endYear":-450,"imprecision":"","text":"2e quart Ve s. av. J.-C.","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"CA 1142","type":"Num\u00e9ro d\u0027entr\u00e9e"},{"value":"CA 4175","type":"Num\u00e9ro d\u0027entr\u00e9e"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s grecques, \u00e9trusques et romaines","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"D\u00e9cor : sur \u00e9paule ; palmette (renvers\u00e9, flanqu\u00e9 de, palmette, 2, oblique, bouton de lotus, 2, surmont\u00e9 de) ; oves (file) \r\nsur panse ; sc\u00e8ne de gyn\u00e9c\u00e9e (?) ; sc\u00e8ne fun\u00e9raire (?, surmont\u00e9 de, m\u00e9andre, restes, entre, filet, 3) ; femme (restes, 2, chit\u00f4n, 1, chit\u00f4n, \u00e0 manche, 1, tenant, branche : feuille, bandelette, 1, de part et d\u0027autre de, table, orn\u00e9 de, branche : feuille, bandelette, restes, 2, ?) ; dans le champ ; alabastre ; l\u00e9cythe\r\n\r\nEtat de l\u0027oeuvre : vase incomplet, recompos\u00e9 de nombreux fragments ; une grosse lacune sur le revers a \u00e9t\u00e9 compl\u00e9t\u00e9e ; le vernis noir est \u00e9caill\u00e9, l\u2019engobe blanc en mauvais \u00e9tat, lacunaire, pulv\u00e9rulent et soulev\u00e9 par endroits ; les lignes de contour sont tr\u00e8s us\u00e9es et partiellement effac\u00e9es ; les visages et les bras des femmes sont rendus par une couche \u00e9paisse de peinture blanche superpos\u00e9e, ainsi que par un rehaut en peinture mate (probablement pourpre)\u00a0 ;  ils sont tr\u00e8s alt\u00e9r\u00e9s et \u00e9caill\u00e9s ; ombreuses concr\u00e9tions.\r\nRestauration : recoll\u00e9","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; une inscription dans le champ\r ; Langue : \r ; grecque\r ; Nature du texte : \r ; acclamation (contenu du texte-\u003Eformule diverse)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"24,6","displayDimension":"24,6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"8,9","displayDimension":"8,9 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":4,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argile\r\nTechnique : peinture brillante (peinture), dessin au trait, fond blanc (peinture), peinture mate (peinture) (?), engobe (?)\r\nPr\u00e9cision technique : peinture brillante noire (col, anse, embouchure, bas de panse, partie sup\u00e9rieure du pied, d\u00e9cor sur l\u0027\u00e9paule, dessin,chiton \u00e0 manches, table, vases dans le champ) ; peinture pourpre (?,chiton, bandeaux) ; engobe blanc (?, chairs de la femme \u00e0 droite)","placeOfCreation":"Ath\u00e8nes","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"\u00c9r\u00e9trie","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Christopoulos","note":"","role":""}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"achat","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date","value":"1899","startYear":1899,"endYear":1899}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s grecques, \u00e9trusques et romaines","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"achat"}],"denomination":[{"value":"l\u00e9cythe"}],"material":[{"value":"argile"}],"technic":[{"value":"dessin au trait"},{"value":"engobe"},{"value":"fond blanc"},{"value":"peinture brillante"},{"value":"peinture m